0.page_description: This is the customer creation form in QuickBooks Online. The form is divided into collapsible sections, with 'Name and contact' and 'Addresses' sections currently visible. The 'Name and contact' section contains fields for title, first name, middle name, last name, suffix, company name, customer display name (marked as required with an asterisk), email, phone number, CC, BCC, mobile number, fax, other contact information, website, and name to print on checks. There's also a checkbox for 'Is a sub-customer'. The 'Addresses' section contains fields for billing address including street address, city, state, ZIP code, and country. At the bottom right of the form is a green 'Save' button.
